# Goal: Target position for the gripper
float64 position    # Target position (0.0 = fully open, 1.0 = fully closed)
float64 max_effort  # Maximum effort to apply (optional, default uses gripper limit)
---
# Result: Final state after execution
float64 position    # Final position achieved
float64 effort      # Final effort applied
bool stalled        # True if gripper stalled before reaching target
bool reached_goal   # True if target position was reached
---
# Feedback: Current state during execution
float64 position    # Current position
float64 effort      # Current effort
bool stalled        # True if gripper is stalled 